</emphasis>
, A. Male pedipalpus, prolateral view; B. Same, ventral view; C. Same, retrolateral view; D. Epigynum, ventral view; E, F. Vulva, dorsal view (specimens from Biyundong Cave, Guizhou); G. Male cheliceral teeth, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.2 mm.
